03/04/87  Login Server

The login server listens on one or more network endpoints for requests
to login to Multics.  The start_login_service request begins listening
on a particular endpoint, and the stop_login_service discontinues
listening.


Other requests: Several requests are available in the login service
environment.

Type "?" for a list of available requests.
Type "list_requests" for a short description of the requests.
Type "list_help" for a list of topics available to the help request.
Type "help TOPIC" for more information on a given topic.
